        "comment": {
            "name": "comment",
            "type": "com.atlassian.jira.issue.fields.CommentSystemField",
            "value": [
                {
                    "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/comment\/35024",
                    "author": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=ajlozier",
                        "name": "ajlozier",
                        "displayName": "Aaron Lozier",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "body": "The attached file contains what seems to be a fix for the reported issue.  Here is what I added:\n\nLines 93-96: added _isAllowedPrivilege parameter.  this serves the same purpose as _isAllowedRole and _isAllowedResource directly above.\n\nLines 762-765: sets _isAllowedPrivilege to $privilege where $privilege not null.  again, same as the functionality for role and resource directly above.\n\nLine 1047: changed $privilege to $this->_isAllowedPrivilege\n\nThe main point here is that wherever null value ('all-privileges') is used in the allow() function, the original value of privilege gets lost in the loop by the time it calls the assertion class.  Saving it in a class parameter and passing that when the assertion class is called resolves the problem.\n\nHope this helps!",
                    "updateAuthor": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=ajlozier",
                        "name": "ajlozier",
                        "displayName": "Aaron Lozier",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "created": "2009-09-30T15:06:27.000+0000",
                    "updated": "2009-09-30T15:06:27.000+0000"
                },
                {
                    "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/comment\/35099",
                    "author": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=ajlozier",
                        "name": "ajlozier",
                        "displayName": "Aaron Lozier",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "body": "_isAllowedPrivilege must also be set back to null at beginning of isAllowed method. Lines 741-742\n\nFROM:\n\n    \t\/\/ reset role & resource to null\n    \t$this->_isAllowedRole = $this->_isAllowedResource = null;\n\nTO:\n\n    \t\/\/ reset role & resource & privilege to null\n    \t$this->_isAllowedRole = $this->_isAllowedResource = $this->_isAllowedPrivilege = null;\n",
                    "updateAuthor": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=ajlozier",
                        "name": "ajlozier",
                        "displayName": "Aaron Lozier",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "created": "2009-10-06T14:54:54.000+0000",
